Dialogue: 2,0:00:59.16,0:01:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\i1}In stores now.{\i0}  {In clear engrish}
Dialogue: 2,0:01:01.70,0:01:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's so pretty...!
Dialogue: 2,0:01:03.84,0:01:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Is this... really me?
Dialogue: 2,0:01:06.75,0:01:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}For one of Seed Records' new artists...
Dialogue: 2,0:01:09.54,0:01:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...they put in a little extra for the TV ad.
Dialogue: 2,0:01:12.76,0:01:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}But... I wonder if everyone will really buy it...
Dialogue: 2,0:01:15.30,0:01:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Losing confidence in your first sales attempt is a problem.
Dialogue: 2,0:01:18.93,0:01:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}There's no mistake... it's a good song.
Dialogue: 2,0:01:21.04,0:01:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's going to be a smashing success!
Dialogue: 1,0:01:24.35,0:01:29.36,Episode Title,,0,0,0,Episode Title,{\pos(322,340)\bord2.5}Is It Really a Hit?
Dialogue: 2,0:01:32.41,0:01:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah... man!
Dialogue: 2,0:01:33.82,0:01:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Just calm down... calm down!
Dialogue: 2,0:01:36.58,0:01:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Until I hear about the sales from Ooshige-san...
Dialogue: 2,0:01:38.78,0:01:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...I can't calm down.
Dialogue: 2,0:01:41.26,0:01:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Man... give me a break.
Dialogue: 2,0:01:43.54,0:01:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hurry up and call, Manager!
Dialogue: 2,0:01:46.87,0:01:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's here!
Dialogue: 2,0:01:50.26,0:01:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hello?
Dialogue: 2,0:01:51.67,0:01:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yes.
Dialogue: 2,0:01:52.47,0:01:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Is that so?
Dialogue: 2,0:01:53.68,0:01:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I understand.
Dialogue: 2,0:01:59.01,0:01:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}How...
Dialogue: 2,0:01:59.51,0:02:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...did it go? {continuation of Meroko from Takuto}
Dialogue: 2,0:02:03.14,0:02:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Um... that's... uh...
Dialogue: 2,0:02:05.13,0:02:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Maybe it's a slow seller.
Dialogue: 2,0:02:07.19,0:02:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It only stared selling yesterday, right?
Dialogue: 2,0:02:09.38,0:02:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}We've only begun the fight, right?
Dialogue: 2,0:02:12.82,0:02:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}All right!
Dialogue: 2,0:02:13.94,0:02:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's a smashing hit!
Dialogue: 2,0:02:15.36,0:02:16.49,Sync,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah?
Dialogue: 2,0:02:17.37,0:02:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}They're receiving orders...
Dialogue: 2,0:02:18.84,0:02:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...the sales are still going!
Dialogue: 2,0:02:20.58,0:02:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What's that...
Dialogue: 2,0:02:21.81,0:02:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...you had us worried...
Dialogue: 2,0:02:23.72,0:02:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}This means that...
Dialogue: 2,0:02:24.70,0:02:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...lots of people are going to \Nhear my song, right?
Dialogue: 2,0:02:28.59,0:02:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}If you had my cunning...
Dialogue: 2,0:02:30.04,0:02:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...you'd sell even more.
Dialogue: 2,0:02:31.82,0:02:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}A {\i1}million seller{\i0}... without a doubt!
Dialogue: 2,0:02:34.30,0:02:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 2,0:02:37.68,0:02:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Isn't it great..?{}
Dialogue: 2,0:02:39.60,0:02:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}After today...
Dialogue: 2,0:02:41.03,0:02:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...talk about {\i1}Full Moon{\i0}  will be everywhere.
Dialogue: 2,0:02:44.41,0:02:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's right!
Dialogue: 2,0:02:45.35,0:02:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You should take your CD to school today!
Dialogue: 2,0:02:48.44,0:02:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh?!
Dialogue: 2,0:02:49.77,0:02:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You can brag and say, "I have {\i1}Full Moon's{\i0}  CD!"
Dialogue: 2,0:02:52.98,0:02:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Maybe...
Dialogue: 2,0:02:53.86,0:02:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It'd be nice if I could do that...
Dialogue: 2,0:02:55.71,0:02:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Everyone will want it!
Dialogue: 2,0:02:57.49,0:03:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah. If that's going to happen, then I should practice my signature first.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:00.61,0:03:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You know...
Dialogue: 2,0:03:01.82,0:03:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}The one who's selling isn't you, it's {\i1}Full Moon...{\i0}
Dialogue: 2,0:03:04.12,0:03:05.14,Overlap,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hey, hey, hey!
Dialogue: 2,0:03:05.14,0:03:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Do you think a ribbon would make me look cuter? {Shani: actually she is talking about her signature here and not herself, so it should be "it" instead of "me", oh well, I guess it will create confusion, so I am leaving it as is.}
Dialogue: 2,0:03:07.83,0:03:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hey... what do you think?
Dialogue: 2,0:03:10.33,0:03:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Meroko, cut it out already...
