Dialogue: 2,0:03:36.32,0:03:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What is it?
Dialogue: 2,0:03:37.70,0:03:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'm thinking about what they all might say...
Dialogue: 2,0:03:39.94,0:03:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}My heart's pounding.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:41.87,0:03:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I wonder if they really heard {\i1}Myself...{\i0}{going crazy over sales results! :D}
Dialogue: 2,0:03:45.58,0:03:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's fine. After all...
Dialogue: 2,0:03:46.99,0:03:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...it was a smashing hit, right?
Dialogue: 2,0:03:48.56,0:03:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Have some faith in yourself.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:50.04,0:03:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's right.
