Dialogue: 2,0:03:56.63,0:03:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It looks like... I've calmed down a bit.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:58.74,0:03:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Then, you're ready.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:59.67,0:04:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yep!
Dialogue: 2,0:04:01.72,0:04:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Good morning!
Dialogue: 2,0:04:03.07,0:04:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah...
Dialogue: 2,0:04:03.43,0:04:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Good morning, Kouyama-san!
Dialogue: 2,0:04:05.01,0:04:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Good morning!
Dialogue: 2,0:04:06.55,0:04:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}And... just earlier...
Dialogue: 2,0:04:07.60,0:04:08.77,Overlap,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Morning!
Dialogue: 2,0:04:08.98,0:04:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Morning, Kumi!
Dialogue: 2,0:04:10.73,0:04:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Geez, Kumi.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:11.60,0:04:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You're in a hurry today.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:13.28,0:04:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Whatever...
Dialogue: 2,0:04:14.27,0:04:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Anyways, did you hear the new single that came out yesterday?
Dialogue: 2,0:04:18.95,0:04:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I heard it. I heard it!
Dialogue: 2,0:04:20.11,0:04:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}The vocal for it was the best! {Vocals?}
Dialogue: 2,0:04:21.99,0:04:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Um...
Dialogue: 2,0:04:23.62,0:04:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\i1}Fu...{\i0}
Dialogue: 2,0:04:24.58,0:04:25.20,Sync,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\i1}Fu...{\i0}
Dialogue: 2,0:04:25.66,0:04:26.53,Sync,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\i1}Fu...{\i0}
Dialogue: 2,0:04:26.53,0:04:27.20,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Full Moon.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:28.21,0:04:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's {\i1}Full Moon{\i0}.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:30.46,0:04:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Furuta!
Dialogue: 2,0:04:32.04,0:04:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}From the {\i1}Guitar Fighters?{\i0}
Dialogue: 2,0:04:33.25,0:04:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's it!
Dialogue: 2,0:04:34.46,0:04:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Maijima-san sure knows \Nwhat she's talking about.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:37.26,0:04:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Of course!
Dialogue: 2,0:04:38.38,0:04:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I keep up to date on all the new songs.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:39.98,0:04:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Really, Chia-san?
Dialogue: 2,0:04:41.16,0:04:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What's she doing?
Dialogue: 2,0:04:42.69,0:04:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}She's supposed to go tell them...
Dialogue: 2,0:04:44.26,0:04:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yeah.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:46.64,0:04:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hey, on TV yesterday...
Dialogue: 2,0:04:49.64,0:04:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I was so surprised... she was so pretty...
Dialogue: 2,0:04:52.63,0:04:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You're talking about \Nthe entertainment news, right?
Dialogue: 2,0:04:55.19,0:04:57.73,Sync,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}The Mashiba "Is that an alien?" Girl!
Dialogue: 2,0:05:03.99,0:05:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What's wrong, Kouyama-san?
Dialogue: 2,0:05:05.82,0:05:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Are you feeling sick again?
Dialogue: 2,0:05:08.45,0:05:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I-It's nothing.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:11.21,0:05:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Thanks.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:12.37,0:05:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Really.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:13.25,0:05:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's good, I guess...
Dialogue: 2,0:05:27.68,0:05:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Nobody's talking about me at all...
Dialogue: 2,0:05:33.14,0:05:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}If you're that concerned about it...
Dialogue: 2,0:05:34.77,0:05:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Don't bother yourself with gossip.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:36.48,0:05:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Why don't you try asking someone yourself?
Dialogue: 2,0:05:39.44,0:05:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Because...
Dialogue: 2,0:05:41.20,0:05:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It couldn't be that... \Nyou don't have any friends?
Dialogue: 2,0:05:45.28,0:05:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Of course not!
Dialogue: 2,0:05:47.13,0:05:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's been two years since \Nshe transferred here.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:50.62,0:05:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's just as Takuto said.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:52.75,0:05:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I've been absent a lot due to my illness, after all.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:57.21,0:05:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}My health has only been getting worse...
Dialogue: 2,0:06:00.16,0:06:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...and I am not allowed to watch \NTV much either, so... {"such unladylike behavior! Wanting to watch tv!" Poor Girl. T_T}{rephrased}
Dialogue: 2,0:06:02.28,0:06:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...I don't have anything to talk about.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:03.81,0:06:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's why... I've never been able to make close friends.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:08.26,0:06:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I see...
Dialogue: 2,0:06:09.32,0:06:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Sorry...
Dialogue: 2,0:06:11.22,0:06:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's okay.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:12.27,0:06:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}As long as I'm selling...
Dialogue: 2,0:06:13.88,0:06:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Everyone will be listening to me...
Dialogue: 2,0:06:15.73,0:06:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...so I can't just dwell in the past.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:18.11,0:06:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'm sorry, too, for making you worry.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:24.66,0:06:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Geez...
Dialogue: 2,0:06:36.13,0:06:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Uh... Ah...?
Dialogue: 2,0:06:38.50,0:06:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah?
Dialogue: 2,0:06:40.96,0:06:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah! This is it!
Dialogue: 2,0:06:43.13,0:06:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Wh-What's with you all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 2,0:06:44.88,0:06:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Look at this!
Dialogue: 2,0:06:46.18,0:06:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{NO TS?}
Dialogue: 2,0:06:46.18,0:06:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Lunchtime broadcast inside the school.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:48.00,0:06:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Taking song requests?{edited}
Dialogue: 2,0:06:49.80,0:06:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What's this?
Dialogue: 2,0:06:51.27,0:06:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}During our lunch break...
Dialogue: 2,0:06:52.38,0:06:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}We have a broadcast DJ...
Dialogue: 2,0:06:54.03,0:06:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}A lot of songs are played, and there's a lot of talking, too.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:57.02,0:06:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's pretty popular.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:59.23,0:07:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Like I said...
Dialogue: 2,0:07:00.23,0:07:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's it!
Dialogue: 2,0:07:00.98,0:07:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh?
Dialogue: 2,0:07:02.23,0:07:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Geez... you're so slow...
Dialogue: 2,0:07:04.11,0:07:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}If nobody's heard you before...
Dialogue: 2,0:07:05.61,0:07:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...then we'll let them hear you.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:08.62,0:07:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh?!!!
Dialogue: 2,0:07:10.28,0:07:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's what we'll do.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:11.79,0:07:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's okay if we broadcast your CD, right?
Dialogue: 2,0:07:15.00,0:07:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I guess so...
Dialogue: 2,0:07:17.42,0:07:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}But...
Dialogue: 2,0:07:18.29,0:07:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah! Geez!
Dialogue: 2,0:07:19.40,0:07:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You're so frustrating!
Dialogue: 2,0:07:20.46,0:07:21.96,Overlap,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}If you don't do anything about it...
Dialogue: 2,0:07:21.96,0:07:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...you'll never make it in the market.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:24.05,0:07:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's easy to give up, but...
Dialogue: 2,0:07:25.80,0:07:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...try working a little harder first!
Dialogue: 2,0:07:28.21,0:07:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}He's right.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:29.30,0:07:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You finally managed to debut.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:35.22,0:07:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's right...
Dialogue: 2,0:07:36.32,0:07:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Maybe I should try working a little harder...
Dialogue: 2,0:07:38.18,0:07:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's not {\i1}"maybe I should try..."{\i0}
Dialogue: 2,0:07:39.81,0:07:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's "I'm gonna work hard!"
Dialogue: 2,0:07:41.96,0:07:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 2,0:07:43.03,0:07:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I haven't even thought about whether or not to request it!
Dialogue: 2,0:07:46.77,0:07:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You're still saying that?!
Dialogue: 2,0:07:48.36,0:07:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}If that's the case...
Dialogue: 2,0:07:54.66,0:07:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Mero Mero Magic!
Dialogue: 2,0:08:01.66,0:08:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:02.34,0:08:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}My CD...
Dialogue: 2,0:08:04.05,0:08:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'm going to request this!
Dialogue: 2,0:08:06.09,0:08:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Meroko, wait!
Dialogue: 2,0:08:07.67,0:08:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You idiot!
Dialogue: 2,0:08:10.01,0:08:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I said wait up!
Dialogue: 2,0:08:12.76,0:08:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Please wait!
Dialogue: 2,0:08:15.27,0:08:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Look... isn't that Kouyama-san?
Dialogue: 2,0:08:17.30,0:08:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What's with her?
Dialogue: 2,0:08:18.88,0:08:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What a weird girl.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:19.96,0:08:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}She's so strange.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:21.94,0:08:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah... th-thanks...
Dialogue: 2,0:08:23.28,0:08:26.52,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah... everyone's laughing at me...
Dialogue: 2,0:08:26.91,0:08:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}She's done it now... that Meroko...
Dialogue: 2,0:08:29.23,0:08:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Meroko, geez!
Dialogue: 2,0:08:31.11,0:08:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Stop!
Dialogue: 2,0:08:32.40,0:08:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Stop already, Meroko!
Dialogue: 2,0:08:35.57,0:08:38.08,Notice,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\fscx103\fscy103\blur0.5\frz328\move(404.634,145,395.617,145,0,2510)}{\t(0,2510,\fscx119\fscy119)}Broadcast Room{Re-TSed}
Dialogue: 2,0:08:36.20,0:08:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's the broadcasting room isn't it?
Dialogue: 2,0:08:44.71,0:08:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Don't just suddenly stop!
Dialogue: 2,0:08:44.71,0:08:46.96,Overlap,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Don't just suddenly stop!
Dialogue: 2,0:08:47.17,0:08:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:08:48.09,0:08:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Kouyama-san... why are you down there?
Dialogue: 2,0:08:51.84,0:08:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ma-Maijima-san!{}
Dialogue: 2,0:08:53.63,0:08:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Okay?
Dialogue: 2,0:08:54.51,0:08:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}For the broadcast...
Dialogue: 2,0:08:55.89,0:08:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Say, "I want to request this", 'kay?
Dialogue: 2,0:08:58.24,0:08:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Oh well...
Dialogue: 2,0:08:59.47,0:09:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}If it's come to this... just give in.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:01.60,0:09:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Are you okay?
Dialogue: 2,0:09:03.16,0:09:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah... um...
Dialogue: 2,0:09:04.61,0:09:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That...
Dialogue: 2,0:09:06.32,0:09:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Um...
Dialogue: 2,0:09:07.27,0:09:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Well...
Dialogue: 2,0:09:08.86,0:09:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah... geez!
Dialogue: 2,0:09:12.03,0:09:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}No!
Dialogue: 2,0:09:13.53,0:09:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What?
Dialogue: 2,0:09:14.49,0:09:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Just hush, 'kay?
Dialogue: 2,0:09:16.16,0:09:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Play {\i1}Myself!{\i0}
Dialogue: 2,0:09:18.07,0:09:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I mean...
Dialogue: 2,0:09:18.95,0:09:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Please play{\i1} Myself.{\i0}
Dialogue: 2,0:09:21.58,0:09:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}'kay?
Dialogue: 2,0:09:22.33,0:09:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}'kay?
Dialogue: 2,0:09:22.66,0:09:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's okay, right?
Dialogue: 2,0:09:23.37,0:09:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}'kay?
Dialogue: 2,0:09:22.79,0:09:23.83,Overlap,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Meroko...{Overlap}
Dialogue: 2,0:09:24.92,0:09:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:09:25.97,0:09:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I wonder what Kouyama-san's doing...
Dialogue: 2,0:09:28.20,0:09:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Is she fighting with Maijima-san?
Dialogue: 2,0:09:31.00,0:09:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Cut it out, Meroko!
Dialogue: 2,0:09:32.84,0:09:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's because you have to request it!
Dialogue: 2,0:09:33.92,0:09:35.84,Overlap,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Will you just cut it out!
Dialogue: 2,0:09:39.81,0:09:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Um...
Dialogue: 2,0:09:40.46,0:09:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Kouyama-san... just what was that?
Dialogue: 2,0:09:44.77,0:09:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'm very sorry!
Dialogue: 2,0:09:49.61,0:09:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Oh man...
Dialogue: 2,0:09:53.20,0:09:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Kouyama-san?
Dialogue: 2,0:09:54.32,0:09:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Are you okay?
Dialogue: 2,0:09:55.45,0:09:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Only strange things are happening to me...
Dialogue: 2,0:09:58.47,0:10:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I can't take it anymore...
Dialogue: 2,0:10:20.27,0:10:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah...
Dialogue: 2,0:10:21.30,0:10:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I didn't give her the CD...
Dialogue: 2,0:10:23.27,0:10:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Nothing's changed...
Dialogue: 2,0:10:24.52,0:10:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}This sucks...
Dialogue: 2,0:10:25.86,0:10:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You said it...
Dialogue: 2,0:10:27.02,0:10:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Who's fault do you think it is?
Dialogue: 2,0:10:29.69,0:10:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah?
Dialogue: 2,0:10:31.76,0:10:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Maijima-san.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:34.53,0:10:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}This is your chance.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:35.61,0:10:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}This is your chance, so go \Nand try requesting again!
Dialogue: 2,0:10:39.45,0:10:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I wonder if it is...
Dialogue: 2,0:10:40.57,0:10:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Of course it is!
Dialogue: 2,0:10:41.66,0:10:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah......
Dialogue: 2,0:10:43.91,0:10:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah...
Dialogue: 2,0:10:44.87,0:10:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Um... Maijima-san...{name correction}
Dialogue: 2,0:10:49.79,0:10:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yes.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:50.17,0:10:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hello?
Dialogue: 2,0:10:51.30,0:10:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You know...
Dialogue: 2,0:10:52.04,0:10:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Maybe she was buying{\i1} Myself?{\i0}
Dialogue: 2,0:10:55.59,0:10:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Don't just stand there \Nand say irresponsible things!
Dialogue: 2,0:10:59.55,0:11:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Because, look at that.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:07.81,0:11:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:08.60,0:11:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\i1}Myself?{\i0}
Dialogue: 2,0:11:09.53,0:11:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\i1}Full Moon's?{\i0}
Dialogue: 2,0:11:10.82,0:11:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}See!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:12.27,0:11:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Absolutely...
Dialogue: 2,0:11:13.53,0:11:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...hopeless.{}
Dialogue: 2,0:11:14.44,0:11:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh?
Dialogue: 2,0:11:16.78,0:11:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yep, Yep.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:18.28,0:11:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}By the way...
Dialogue: 2,0:11:19.14,0:11:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'm going with my mother to Shibuya tomorrow.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:21.37,0:11:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'm looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:22.79,0:11:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1\i1}"Hopeless..."{\i0}{edited for continuation}
Dialogue: 2,0:11:24.00,0:11:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What does she mean?
Dialogue: 2,0:11:30.75,0:11:33.71,Notice2,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(314.993,222)}Kouyama
Dialogue: 2,0:11:31.12,0:11:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'm home.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:36.30,0:11:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Well...
Dialogue: 2,0:11:37.42,0:11:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}How did you get that injury?
Dialogue: 2,0:11:39.92,0:11:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}This is...
Dialogue: 2,0:11:44.31,0:11:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Lately, you've...
Dialogue: 2,0:11:45.91,0:11:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...been joking around and acting rather flippant, you know.{edited}
Dialogue: 2,0:11:51.14,0:11:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You have to consider your health, so...
Dialogue: 2,0:11:53.00,0:11:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...be more careful from now on.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:54.94,0:11:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Do you understand?
Dialogue: 2,0:11:57.88,0:11:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yes...
Dialogue: 2,0:12:06.08,0:12:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Wow!
Dialogue: 2,0:12:07.01,0:12:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}This taiyaki...!
Dialogue: 2,0:12:08.16,0:12:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's {\i1}sooo{\i0}  good!
Dialogue: 2,0:12:09.37,0:12:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Come on! Come on!
Dialogue: 2,0:12:10.12,0:12:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It smells good, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 2,0:12:11.37,0:12:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Well? Well? Well?
Dialogue: 2,0:12:11.91,0:12:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Look!
Dialogue: 2,0:12:12.58,0:12:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I don't want any.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:13.79,0:12:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What are you saying?!
Dialogue: 2,0:12:15.29,0:12:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}The tail is filled with anko...
Dialogue: 2,0:12:17.29,0:12:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's refreshing.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:19.63,0:12:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's right!
Dialogue: 2,0:12:20.13,0:12:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You'll regret it if you don't have any!
Dialogue: 2,0:12:21.97,0:12:22.34,Overlap,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Come on!
Dialogue: 2,0:12:22.34,0:12:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Come on! Come on!
Dialogue: 2,0:12:22.93,0:12:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Come on! Come on!
Dialogue: 2,0:12:23.55,0:12:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Well?
Dialogue: 2,0:12:23.55,0:12:24.05,Overlap,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Come on!{}
Dialogue: 2,0:12:24.05,0:12:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Well? Well? Well?
Dialogue: 2,0:12:24.84,0:12:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\pos(562,450)}Well?
Dialogue: 2,0:12:24.84,0:12:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\pos(74,450)}Well?
Dialogue: 2,0:12:24.84,0:12:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Geez!
Dialogue: 2,0:12:25.64,0:12:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I don't want any means I don't want any!
Dialogue: 2,0:12:27.76,0:12:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah?
Dialogue: 2,0:12:35.52,0:12:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yes?
Dialogue: 2,0:12:36.69,0:12:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah. Mitsuki?
Dialogue: 2,0:12:38.03,0:12:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's Ooshige.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:39.61,0:12:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}There's already a huge response for{\i1} Myself.{\i0}
Dialogue: 2,0:12:42.78,0:12:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\fscx90\fscy90}The CD shop has already sent additional orders.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:45.65,0:12:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\fscx90\fscy90}It's the first time one of my talents\N has been such a huge hit!{line break}
Dialogue: 2,0:12:49.87,0:12:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You said it's a hit, but...
Dialogue: 2,0:12:51.16,0:12:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...is it really?
Dialogue: 2,0:12:53.00,0:12:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Of course!
Dialogue: 2,0:12:54.68,0:12:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}The radio and television stations want an interview as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:58.17,0:12:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}They've all been asking for one.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:59.84,0:13:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Can you hear it?
Dialogue: 2,0:13:00.50,0:13:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}All the phones here are going off.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:03.18,0:13:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Is that so?
Dialogue: 2,0:13:04.72,0:13:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}But... nobody knows about it...
Dialogue: 2,0:13:06.76,0:13:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\fscx90\fscy90}Eh?
Dialogue: 2,0:13:07.26,0:13:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\fscx90\fscy90}Mitsuki?
Dialogue: 2,0:13:07.97,0:13:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\fscx90\fscy90}Hello?
Dialogue: 2,0:13:08.97,0:13:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\fscx90\fscy90}Mitsuki?
Dialogue: 2,0:13:09.26,0:13:10.39,Overlap,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's nothing.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:10.85,0:13:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:15.69,0:13:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Your manager is going to worry about you.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:17.94,0:13:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Because...!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:18.65,0:13:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Even though nobody's heard it...
Dialogue: 2,0:13:20.09,0:13:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...why does she say it's a hit?!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:22.28,0:13:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's because...
Dialogue: 2,0:13:23.37,0:13:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}But... there hasn't been \Nmuch publicity for it...
Dialogue: 2,0:13:26.11,0:13:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Even if there was publicity, \Nno one would listen to it!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:28.63,0:13:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's useless!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:30.00,0:13:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Besides...
Dialogue: 2,0:13:31.83,0:13:33.58,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah..."Myself"?
Dialogue: 2,0:13:33.58,0:13:34.46,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Full Moon's?
Dialogue: 2,0:13:35.04,0:13:36.31,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Absolutely...
Dialogue: 2,0:13:36.31,0:13:37.33,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...hopeless.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:41.63,0:13:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Sorry.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:42.89,0:13:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Can you leave me alone for a bit?
Dialogue: 2,0:13:45.93,0:13:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Don't come to school anymore either.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:54.36,0:13:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'm leaving.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:01.27,0:14:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Good morning!
Dialogue: 2,0:14:02.11,0:14:03.36,Overlap,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Oh! Good morning!
Dialogue: 2,0:14:02.98,0:14:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Good morning!
Dialogue: 2,0:14:10.45,0:14:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}For some reason... I don't think I'll make it...
Dialogue: 2,0:14:12.74,0:14:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What are you saying after coming this far?
Dialogue: 2,0:14:14.43,0:14:14.83,Overlap,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah?
Dialogue: 2,0:14:17.12,0:14:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Takuto!
Dialogue: 2,0:14:18.21,0:14:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:19.29,0:14:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'm sorry about yesterday.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:21.04,0:14:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's okay.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:22.26,0:14:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Anyways, don't get hung up over something like that.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:24.28,0:14:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You can't act like before from now on.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:26.55,0:14:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's because...
Dialogue: 2,0:14:27.42,0:14:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I thought everyone would be \Ntalking about {\i1}Full Moon!{\i0}
Dialogue: 2,0:14:30.61,0:14:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yet everyone... Even after\N I put all I had into it...{edited}
Dialogue: 2,0:14:33.43,0:14:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You know...{}
Dialogue: 2,0:14:34.53,0:14:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}If you want them to hear you sing, then sing for them yourself!
Dialogue: 2,0:14:37.64,0:14:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You want to be friends with them after all!{edited}
Dialogue: 2,0:14:39.44,0:14:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}If you don't tell them yourself...
Dialogue: 2,0:14:41.44,0:14:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...they won't be your friends.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:44.48,0:14:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Sing together?
Dialogue: 2,0:14:46.32,0:14:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Like I said...
Dialogue: 2,0:14:47.95,0:14:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}The fact that you don't have \Nany girls you're close to.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:49.78,0:14:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Before you can even start worrying about how you can't talk to anyone...
Dialogue: 2,0:14:52.00,0:14:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Smile and try to talk to them yourself first!
Dialogue: 2,0:14:56.20,0:14:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I see...
Dialogue: 2,0:14:57.33,0:14:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Sing together, huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:14:59.02,0:14:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's right.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:59.82,0:15:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Anyways, give it a try.{edited}
Dialogue: 2,0:15:01.52,0:15:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I wonder if I can do it.
Dialogue: 2,0:15:03.29,0:15:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I told you yesterday, right?
Dialogue: 2,0:15:04.44,0:15:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}In times like this...
Dialogue: 2,0:15:08.01,0:15:09.32,Sync,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Take a deep breath.
Dialogue: 2,0:15:11.18,0:15:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's right.
Dialogue: 2,0:15:12.64,0:15:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I should smile myself.
Dialogue: 2,0:15:15.39,0:15:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Come. Come. {Oh no she didn't}
Dialogue: 2,0:15:16.35,0:15:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Check this out. Look at this.
Dialogue: 2,0:15:18.98,0:15:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That voice is...
Dialogue: 2,0:15:20.56,0:15:21.56,Sync,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Meroko!
Dialogue: 2,0:15:22.15,0:15:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What we have here is...
Dialogue: 2,0:15:24.19,0:15:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It just went on sale yesterday... {Oh yes she did}{Shani: Meroko is so damn awesome!}
Dialogue: 2,0:15:27.78,0:15:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Right now...
Dialogue: 2,0:15:28.61,0:15:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}There's a mad rush to acquire this huge hit...
Dialogue: 2,0:15:30.57,0:15:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's crazy! {Kwayzyyyyyy}
Dialogue: 2,0:15:31.57,0:15:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Which means...
Dialogue: 2,0:15:32.41,0:15:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's something you can't easily get! {Is it drugs?}
Dialogue: 2,0:15:35.08,0:15:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Over here...
Dialogue: 2,0:15:36.00,0:15:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Don't just sit there studying \Nwith your buddies...
Dialogue: 2,0:15:41.10,0:15:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Come!
Dialogue: 2,0:15:42.00,0:15:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Buy it! Buy it!
Dialogue: 2,0:15:44.55,0:15:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Those are... my CDs...{edited}{copyright infringement :D}
Dialogue: 2,0:15:46.42,0:15:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What the hell is she doing?
Dialogue: 2,0:15:48.16,0:15:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Kouyama-san somehow become quite a character all of a sudden.
Dialogue: 2,0:15:51.43,0:15:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I never thought she was \Nthis kind of a person. {edited}
Dialogue: 2,0:15:54.05,0:15:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yeah.
Dialogue: 2,0:15:54.55,0:15:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's totally different from her image.
Dialogue: 2,0:15:57.02,0:15:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You're horrible...
Dialogue: 2,0:15:58.07,0:15:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You're horrible, Meroko! {Shani: WHOA! I almost feared she gave it away that Meroko was her double there, mattaku mo...}
Dialogue: 2,0:16:03.48,0:16:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What were you thinking? {For shame}
Dialogue: 2,0:16:05.65,0:16:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Because...
Dialogue: 2,0:16:07.57,0:16:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I thought I was kinda wrong yesterday...
Dialogue: 2,0:16:11.53,0:16:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}If you're regretting it...
Dialogue: 2,0:16:13.05,0:16:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Why did you pretend to be her?
Dialogue: 2,0:16:15.24,0:16:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}If they listen to {\i1}Full Moon's{\i0}  song...
Dialogue: 2,0:16:17.73,0:16:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...Mitsuki will be able to make lots of friends, won't she?
Dialogue: 2,0:16:21.81,0:16:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Even if that was your goal, \Nyour methods were wrong!{edited}
Dialogue: 2,0:16:25.01,0:16:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I thought that was the best way \Nto get their attention.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:27.92,0:16:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You know...
Dialogue: 2,0:16:28.75,0:16:29.30,Overlap,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's alright.{edited}
Dialogue: 2,0:16:29.64,0:16:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's okay, Takuto.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:31.63,0:16:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh?
Dialogue: 2,0:16:32.89,0:16:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's enough...
Dialogue: 2,0:16:34.01,0:16:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Well...
Dialogue: 2,0:16:34.93,0:16:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Meroko was doing it for my sake, too.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:38.89,0:16:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Besides...
Dialogue: 2,0:16:39.56,0:16:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I didn't have friends to begin with, so...
Dialogue: 2,0:16:41.48,0:16:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It won't change the way people think about me.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:44.32,0:16:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah...
Dialogue: 2,0:16:46.86,0:16:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I have to go already.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:57.95,0:17:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I thought it was a good idea...
Dialogue: 2,0:17:00.37,0:17:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hmm?
Dialogue: 2,0:17:04.34,0:17:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah... she's here! She's here!
Dialogue: 2,0:17:06.17,0:17:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Man... we were looking all over\N for you, Kouyama-san.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:08.73,0:17:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh?
Dialogue: 2,0:17:11.92,0:17:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hey, I was wondering if it's okay for me to use this CD during the lunchtime broadcast.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:16.30,0:17:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh?!
Dialogue: 2,0:17:17.04,0:17:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}But...
Dialogue: 2,0:17:17.80,0:17:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You said it was absolutely hopeless yesterday.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:21.31,0:17:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's right.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:22.37,0:17:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}No matter where I went... \NI couldn't get one at all.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:25.92,0:17:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I was even thinking that I'd have to go to Shibuya to find a copy...
Dialogue: 2,0:17:29.19,0:17:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's really popular.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:30.62,0:17:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}The lyrics are great...
Dialogue: 2,0:17:31.77,0:17:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}The song's the best!
Dialogue: 2,0:17:33.49,0:17:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Especially that part.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:34.58,0:17:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Doushite konna ni...
Dialogue: 2,0:17:37.66,0:17:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}No, you're wrong.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:39.34,0:17:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Doushite konna ni...
Dialogue: 2,0:17:41.83,0:17:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That seems kinda off.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:43.20,0:17:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Really?
Dialogue: 2,0:17:44.04,0:17:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'm pretty sure it went like this...
Dialogue: 2,0:17:45.62,0:17:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Doushite konna ni...
Dialogue: 2,0:17:48.72,0:17:51.04,Overlap,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That sounds even more off.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:50.27,0:17:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You think so?
Dialogue: 2,0:17:51.34,0:17:52.92,Overlap,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I wonder how it really went.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:53.35,0:17:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}If I recall...
Dialogue: 2,0:17:56.60,0:17:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Um... um...
Dialogue: 2,0:17:58.72,0:17:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Isn't it like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.48,0:18:08.64,Myself Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}{\pos(320,36)\c&HFFE6B8&\3c&HC1704F&}Doushite konna ni suki nandarou
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.73,0:18:16.32,Myself Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}{\pos(320,36)\c&HFFE6B8&\3c&HC1704F&}Kimi no koe kanashii hodo hibiiteru yo
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.47,0:18:08.65,Myself TL,,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}Why do I love you so?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.73,0:18:16.32,Myself TL,,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}Your voice is calling out with such sadness
Dialogue: 2,0:18:24.04,0:18:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah sorry.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:25.62,0:18:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I shouldn't have done that.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:27.71,0:18:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Amazing.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:28.54,0:18:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Kouyama-san, you're like the real thing.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:30.33,0:18:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You're so cool!
Dialogue: 2,0:18:31.27,0:18:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh?
Dialogue: 2,0:18:31.76,0:18:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I wonder if that's so...
Dialogue: 2,0:18:32.86,0:18:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yeah.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:33.40,0:18:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Kouyama-san, you're good at singing, aren't you?
Dialogue: 2,0:18:35.68,0:18:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's not just singing...
Dialogue: 2,0:18:37.22,0:18:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Her performance earlier.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:38.56,0:18:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah... That was hilarious.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:40.59,0:18:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah... that was...
Dialogue: 2,0:18:40.89,0:18:43.81,Overlap,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I didn't know you had it in you.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:43.93,0:18:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hang out with us more from now on, okay?
Dialogue: 2,0:18:46.10,0:18:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Teach us how to sing, too.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:48.19,0:18:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Okay!
Dialogue: 2,0:18:48.94,0:18:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}If I can do it, I'll sing as much as you want!
Dialogue: 2,0:18:50.77,0:18:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hey, Mitsuki...
Dialogue: 2,0:18:51.67,0:18:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah! It's okay if we call you Mitsuki, right?
Dialogue: 2,0:18:53.73,0:18:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Do you want to come to \Nthe broadcast with me?{line break}
Dialogue: 2,0:18:55.29,0:18:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'll show you how it's done... \Nbroadcasting, that is...{line break}
Dialogue: 2,0:18:57.62,0:18:58.70,Sync,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Let's go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 2,0:18:58.70,0:18:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Okay!
Dialogue: 2,0:18:59.07,0:18:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I want to try it!
Dialogue: 2,0:19:00.29,0:19:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You can call me Tomoe.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:04.03,0:19:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Well, well.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:04.78,0:19:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That takes care of this for now.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:07.04,0:19:07.50,Sync,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah!{}
Dialogue: 2,0:19:08.71,0:19:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Meroko.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:09.50,0:19:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'm sorry for saying mean things to you.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:11.17,0:19:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Takuto, thank you.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:12.67,0:19:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Mitsuki.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:13.34,0:19:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 2,0:19:14.17,0:19:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Oh, I'm coming right away. {she is talking with her friends here}
Dialogue: 2,0:19:15.48,0:19:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Bye! {and this one is with the Negi Ramen}
Dialogue: 2,0:19:18.76,0:19:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}All right!
Dialogue: 2,0:19:19.40,0:19:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Thanks to what I did...
Dialogue: 2,0:19:20.84,0:19:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I don't have to leave, and {\i1}Full Moon{\i0}  won't be sad anymore, right, Takuto? {double space added between "Full Moon" and "won't"}
Dialogue: 2,0:19:24.30,0:19:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You're getting better.
