Dialogue: 2,0:19:30.39,0:19:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Look at this.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:31.81,0:19:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's really selling.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:33.66,0:19:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}The production can't even keep up with it.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:35.50,0:19:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Everyone wants to listen to {\i1}Full Moon's{\i0}  song!
Dialogue: 2,0:19:37.72,0:19:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Believe me! {Believe it!, Oh how I wanted to use this line.}
