Dialogue: 2,0:19:39.83,0:19:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I know.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:40.99,0:19:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Like I said...!
Dialogue: 2,0:19:42.64,0:19:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh?
Dialogue: 2,0:19:43.70,0:19:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I know it very well.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:45.20,0:19:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Lots of people are listening to it.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:47.92,0:19:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}From now on, I'll work harder!{edited}
Dialogue: 2,0:19:51.58,0:19:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Take a deep breath and smile!
