Dialogue: 2,0:21:36.56,0:21:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hmm...
Dialogue: 2,0:21:37.23,0:21:38.86,Overlap,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Takuto, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 2,0:21:38.86,0:21:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That doctor, Wakaouji...{edited}
Dialogue: 2,0:21:40.36,0:21:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What's on his mind?
Dialogue: 2,0:21:41.94,0:21:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}No matter how many times he goes around with Mitsuki...
Dialogue: 2,0:21:43.49,0:21:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}He hasn't heard of {\i1}Myself.{\i0}
Dialogue: 2,0:21:45.28,0:21:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh? Why?
