Dialogue: 2,0:21:50.12,0:21:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Someone said he was \Na musician before, right?
Dialogue: 2,0:21:52.58,0:21:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Is there something else to him?
