Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.13,0:20:00.30,Myself ED2 TL,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fad(200,100)}Why... just why have I fallen in love with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.30,0:20:06.76,Myself ED2 TL,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\be3\fad(200,200)}Yet, still... I can't stop my tears from falling...
