Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.70,0:20:34.62,Myself ED2 TL,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fad(210,100)}That place you had to leave for a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.63,0:20:42.22,Myself ED2 TL,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fad(200,0)}It happened to be the place where I was
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.05,0:20:48.60,Myself ED2 TL,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fad(210,100)}On that day I could see...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.31,0:20:53.44,Myself ED2 TL,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fad(200,0)}The desolation lying in your eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.40,0:20:59.07,Myself ED2 TL,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fad(210,0)}I wonder if it's the same for both of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.23,0:21:06.45,Myself ED2 TL,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fad(210,0)}If you would just notice, I'm always by your side
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.91,0:21:12.54,Myself ED2 TL,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fad(160,0)}Why do I love you so?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.75,0:21:18.54,Myself ED2 TL,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fad(160,0)}Your voice is calling out with such sadness
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.84,0:21:24.63,Myself ED2 TL,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fad(160,42)}I never knew what was supporting me, back then, and even now
